      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This distinguished vehicle represents an exceptional balance of performance and long-term reliability. Meticulously maintained and presenting in commendable condition, it offers a refined driving experience for the discerning owner. Every aspect of its mechanical integrity and aesthetic profile has been preserved to ensure continued excellence on the road. We invite you to experience the quality and sophistication of this well-appointed selection.",
