      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s looking for a brand-new home. It\u2019s been super reliable and is still in great shape for all your daily drives and weekend adventures. It runs smoothly and has been well-loved, so it's ready to hit the road the moment you hop in. Come by and take it for a spin\u2014I think you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
